</ref>
<q xml:lang="ta">ney <c type="geminated">y</c>iḻutu pōṉṟa veḷḷiya niṉattaiyuṭaiya koḻuviya taṭi</q>
<q xml:lang="en">greasy pieces of white fat that resemble butter</q></cit><cit type="commentary"><ref target="https://archive.org/details/kmm-0708-seevaga-sinthamani-1922/page/910/mode/1up">title, poem number, line number</ref>
<q xml:lang="ta">iḻut’ ār pū – tēṉ niṟainta pū</q>
<q xml:lang="en">flower filled with honey</q></cit></entry>
